'''Skotizo''' is a demonic boss located beneath the [[Catacombs of Kourend]]. Accessing his lair requires the use of a [[dark totem]] on the [[Altar (Catacombs of Kourend)|altar]] found in the centre of the Catacombs; one dark totem permits only one attempt, which makes him a [[Sporadic bosses|sporadic boss]].

He is primarily known for his guaranteed [[Clue scroll (hard)|hard clue scroll]] drops, along with a very high chance of [[Clue scroll (elite)|elite clue scrolls]].

Skotizo can be substituted for both [[Black demon]] and [[Greater demon]] kills during Slayer tasks. Skotizo's Lair is part of the Catacombs of Kourend, and '''does''' count as such for the purpose of Konar Slayer tasks. He cannot be damaged with a [[ring of recoil]].

